channel.title: Comments on: Duran Duran “Nite Runner” stream- not just for fatties anymore

item.title: By: KFabulous
item.dc:creator: KFabulous
item.description: Listen to tracks 1-4, and #6 on the RCM album...a few times. I assure you, this CD is infectious in the best possible way. Nite Runner should absolutely be their next release...c'mon guys!
item.content:encoded: Listen to tracks 1-4, and #6 on the RCM album…a few times. I assure you, this CD is infectious in the best possible way. Nite Runner should absolutely be their next release…c’mon guys!

item.title: By: Oscar
item.dc:creator: Oscar
item.description: Love it! Great track! This is definitely cutting edge and with plenty of radio play DD will be back in the limelight again! "Falling Down" will be a great first track. Hope "Red Carpet Masssacre" shines this November 13th.
item.content:encoded: Love it! Great track! This is definitely cutting edge and with plenty of radio play DD will be back in the limelight again! “Falling Down” will be a great first track. Hope “Red Carpet Masssacre” shines this November 13th.
